lished>2024-09-10T16:22:50-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T16:22:50-04:00</updated><title>这就是你的 iPhone 16 最终将用 Apple Intelligence 做的事情</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;带有一点人工智能光芒的苹果标志。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/2EU0w2a1CoSdue3mXMf8ojofHUs=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73577273/247097_Apple__AI__CVirginia_B2B.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;sos7mu&quot;>;苹果大量提及人工智能&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9 /9/24237601/apple-iphone-16-event-announcements-products&quot;>;周一的 iPhone 16 发布会&lt;/a>;。不过，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/31/24209910/apple-intelligence-ios-18-preview-siri&quot;>;生成式 Apple Intelligence 功能&lt;/a>;将不会为 9 月 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240230/ios-18-release-date-iphone-16&quot;>;iOS 18 公开发布&lt;/a>;做好准备16 号或 9 月 20 日发布的新 iPhone 时。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Aw3YxR&quot;>;首批 Apple 人工智能功能计划于下个月在大多数地区（欧盟除外）公开发布。针对 iPhone 15 Pro 和所有 iPhone 16，以及配备 M1 或更高 Apple Silicon 芯片的 Mac 和 iPad 进行 Beta 测试。发布时，它们仅提供美国英语版本。&lt;/p>; &lt;h2 id=&quot;4dVnOo&quot;>;Apple Intelligence 十月份将推出哪些内容&lt;/h2>; &lt;h3 id=&quot;MD8Ayj&quot;>;书写工具&lt;/h3>; &lt;ul>; &lt;li id=&quot;lPgfrh&quot;>; &lt;strong>;文本重写：&lt;/strong>;文本重写会将您的电子邮件写作草稿变成更专业的草稿，您可以将语气更改为友好或...&lt;/ li>; &lt;/ul>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24237714/apple-intelligence-generative-ai-features-update-schedule&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip; &lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24237714/apple-intelligence-generative-ai-features-update-schedule" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24237714/apple-intelligence-generative-ai-features-update-schedule</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-10T15:59:21-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T15:59:21-04:00</updated><title>如何选择购买哪款 Apple Watch</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;在彩色插图背景上渲染各种 Apple Watch 型号。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/2khdyHiysXFCvt1JfQN-z5B3IfA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/70781237/acastro_220321_5154_0001.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge 提供&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;在 Apple Watch Series 10、Ultra 2 和第二代 SE 之间，有比以往更多的选择。我们将帮助您对它们进行分类。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23037217/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-second-gen-se -best-smartwatch-how-to&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23037217/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-second-gen-se-best-smartwatch-how-to" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23037217/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-second-gen-se-best-smartwatch-how-to</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-10T15:44:37-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T15:44:37-04:00</updated><title>美国终于瞄准了卡车膨胀问题</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;行人过马路&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/IcRX_W-kzJrpLQjbL4Trzcc5-Ko=/0x1:4497x2999/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/73577192/2169610326.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Bruce Bennett / Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;UrnuDv&quot;>;本周，美国国家公路交通安全国家公路交通安全管理局 (NHTSA) &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nhtsa.gov/press-releases/nhtsa-proposes-new-vehicle-safety-standard-protect-pedestrians&quot;>;提议新的车辆规则&lt;/ a>; 据称这将有助于减少美国的行人死亡。新规定似乎直接针对SUV和卡车日益大型化的趋势，事实证明，与中小型车辆相比，它们对行人的危害更大。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;G2j8Mo&quot;>;监管机构成立 50 多年以来，从未向汽车制造商发布过新规则，要求他们改变车辆设计，以更好地防止行人死亡。如果颁布，新规则可能会永久改变美国车辆的设计方式。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;zULZJF&quot;>;“很高兴看到 NHTSA 承认短视地关注行人检测（这是不完美的）……&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241047/nhtsa-rule-pedestrian-safety-fmvss-suv-truck-design&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241047/nhtsa-rule-pedestrian-safety-fmvss-suv-truck-design" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241047/nhtsa-rule-pedestrian-safety-fmvss-suv-truck-design</id><author><name>安德鲁·霍金斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-10T15:18:56-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T15:18:56-04:00</updated><title>微软新的 Xbox Game Pass Standard 套餐现已推出，每月价格为 14.99 美元</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Xbox Game Pass 徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/7nmzOqq0E4GlSvVMZt8DUfuDCVE=/112x0:1318x804/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image /image/73577139/Picture2_5fc8caea720af4f20042.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Microsoft&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;9IiyRP&quot;>;微软今天推出其 Xbox Game Pass 标准版。上个月与 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/20/24224498/xbox-game-pass-standard-testing-xbox-insiders&quot;>;Xbox Insider 进行了简要测试&lt;/a >;，每月 14.99 美元的新 Game Pass Standard 订阅 &lt;a href=&quot;https://news.xbox.com/en-us/2024/09/10/xbox-game-pass-standard-is-here/&quot;>;也将与用于 Xbox 和在线控制台多人访问的常用 Game Pass 库一起启动。不过，这个新级别并不包括立即访问第一天发布的游戏。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;7wSusf&quot;>;微软于 7 月份首次透露了这个新的 Xbox Game Pass 标准级别，&lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2024/7/9/24195312/microsoft-xbox-game-pass-ultimate-price-increase-standard-subscription&quot;>;Ultimate 和 PC Game Pass 订阅者的价格上涨&lt;/a>;。主机版 Xbox Game Pass 的现有订阅者将继续能够访问第一天的游戏，但新的 Game Pass 订阅者现在只能在 Core、Standard、PC 和 Ultimate 订阅之间进行选择。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class =&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：...&lt;/cite>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241171/xbox -game-pass-standard-launch-pricing&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241171/xbox-game-pass-standard-launch-pricing" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241171/xbox-game-pass-standard-launch-pricing</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-10T15:16:11-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T15:16:11-04:00</updated><title> ESPN 的人工智能生成的体育赛事回顾已经没有抓住要点</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;ESPN 徽标的矢量插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/W2UsX5VFaS7XthuGJP8h8lx0u0E=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73577137/STK281_ESPN_C.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;whpbCa&quot;>;本周末，ESPN 开始发布人工智能生成的女子足球比赛回顾，并将推出更多体育赛事。它使用微软人工智能来编写每个故事，人类只参与审查每个摘要的“质量和准确性”。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.espnfrontrow.com/2024/09/enhancing-espns-game-recaps-for-underserved-sports-using-ai/&quot;>;ESPN 表示&lt;/a>;这些故事将“增强”，而不是贬低它的其他内容——但不用说，人们对它有感情。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;bm9OTC&quot;>;ESPN 并不是将人工智能工作伪装成人类的工作。事实上，每个故事都宣传自己是由“ESPN Generative AI Services”撰写的，并且 ESPN 在每篇文章的底部都添加了一条注释，说明重述是如何基于体育赛事的记录的。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;nyXmnS&quot;>;ESPN 并不是唯一这样做的新闻机构； &lt;em>;美联社&lt;/em>;开始使用人工智能来撰写体育报道......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24240955/espn -generative-ai-reports-womens-soccer-lacrosse-premier-league&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24240955/espn-generative-ai-reports-womens-soccer-lacrosse-premier-league" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24240955/espn-generative-ai-reports-womens-soccer-lacrosse-premier-league</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-10T14:44:52-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T14:44:52-04:00</updated><title>您无需更换 AirPods Max 即可获得新颜色</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple 的橙色 AirPods Max 耳垫位于原始银色 AirPods Max 上。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Sjtag1-j2xsRMjMm1xk8ifvknH8=/0x1:710x474/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73577047/airpodsmax.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;新颜色选项的 AirPods Max 替换耳垫现已上市。&lt;/em>; |图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;prvtWL&quot;>;如果您羡慕新的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236804/ airpods-max-second-gen-price-specs-features-release-date&quot;>;AirPods Max 颜色&lt;/a>;，但不认为从 Apple 专有的 Lightning 端口切换到 USB-C 足以成为升级的理由，您可以现在购买仍与耳机原始版本兼容的新配色的替换耳垫，如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.macrumors.com/2024/09/10/airpods-max-ear-cushions -in-new-colors/&quot;>;&lt;em>;MacRumors&lt;/em>; 发现了&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;tpMLIp&quot;>;耳垫是&lt;a href=&quot;https://apple. sjv.io/c/482924/435031/7613?subId1=VergeApple091024&amp;amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fshop%2Fproduct%2FMA6G4ZM%2FA%2Fairpods-max-ear-cushions-purple&quot;rel= “赞助的 nofollow noopener” target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;现已在 Apple 在线商店&lt;/a>;上架，蓝色、橙色、紫色、午夜或星光色套装售价 69 美元，预计次日发货。新款 USB-C 版本的 AirPods Max 为 &lt;a href=&quot;https://apple.sjv.io/c/482924/1950761/7613?subId1=VergeAirPodsMaxUSBCNews&amp;amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple。 com%2Fshop%2Fbuy-airpods%2Fairpods-max&amp;subId2=[vg0910awD][24000845][][][][][][][][][https://www.theverge.com/search?q =airpods+max]&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;目前可供预订&lt;/a>;，但要到 9 月 20 日才会发货。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;3w21s5&quot;>;Apple 正在仍在销售 &lt;a href=&quot;https://apple.sjv.io/c/482924/435031/7613?subId1=VergeApple091024&amp;amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fshop%2Fproduct%2FMWUA3ZM%2FA %2Fairpods-max-lightning-connector-ear-cushions-red&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;替换耳垫与 AirPods Max 原始 Lightning 版本的颜色相匹配&lt;/a>;，包括绿色、银色、黑色、天蓝色……&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241034/apple-airpods-max-wireless-headphones -ear-cushions-colors&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241034/apple-airpods-max-wireless-headphones-ear-cushions-colors" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241034/apple-airpods-max-wireless-headphones-ear-cushions-colors</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-10T14:37:46-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T14:37:46-04:00</updated><title> iPhone 16 将作为半成品发货</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;iPhone 16 上的 Apple Intelligence 图像。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/EuCK4G0zVU01Gc_14YNVHEyW_cg=/0x0:2743x1829/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73577034/Apple_iPhone_16_Pro_Apple_Intelligence_personal_context_ 01_240909.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：苹果&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;SwWImF&quot;>;苹果全力投入人工智能——至少是苹果的版本。苹果首席执行官蒂姆·库克在展示 iPhone 16 之前表示：“下一代 iPhone 是从头开始为 Apple Intelligence 设计的。”软件主管 Craig Federighi 将 Apple Intelligence 定位为“个人智能系统”，是“智能手机的核心”。 iPhone 16 系列。”活动结束后，苹果甚至发布了完整的新闻稿&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2024/09/apple-intelligence-comes-to-iphone-ipad-and-mac-starting- next-month/&quot;>;致力于 Apple Intelligence&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;eafJBf&quot;>;只有一个问题：当 iPhone 16 和 16 Pro 首次推出时，它们不会有任何 Apple 信息智能功能。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;LQfcdS&quot;>;当然，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24237017/iphone-16-specs-features 中的新 A18 和 A18 Pro 芯片-price-release-date-apple&quot;>;iPhone 16&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24230103/iphone-16-pro-specs-features-price -release-date-apple&quot;>;阵容&lt;/a>;每个都有一个 16 核神经引擎，苹果称其“针对大型生成模型进行了优化”，因此它们可能会擅长处理&lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/2024/6/10/24175405/wwdc-apple-ai-news-features-ios-18-macos-15-iphone-ipad-mac&quot;>;一个...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p >; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241043/apple-iphone-16-pro-intelligence-ai-missing&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt; /p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241043/apple-iphone-16-pro-intelligence-ai-missing" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241043/apple-iphone-16-pro-intelligence-ai-missing</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry></feed>